      "description": "Looking for an affordable ride or a project car with potential? This vehicle is honestly priced to reflect its well-worn condition \u2014 it shows clear signs of age and heavy use both inside and out, and will likely need some mechanical and cosmetic attention to get it back in top shape. That said, it's a great opportunity for a handy buyer or someone who just needs basic transportation on a tight budget. Come take a look and see if it's the right fit for you!",
      "price": 5500.0,
