      "timestep_posted": 38
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_10_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_10",
      "description": "\ud83d\udd27 Budget-Friendly Fixer-Upper \u2014 Great Opportunity for the Right Buyer! \ud83d\udd27 This vehicle is in poor condition \u2014 it runs, but it comes with notable wear and mechanical issues that will need attention. You'll find significant cosmetic damage on the exterior, and there are mechanical concerns that should be addressed before relying on it for regular use. That said, it's priced to reflect exactly what it is \u2014 an honest, no-surprises deal for a hands-on buyer, a parts car, or someone looking for an affordable project! If you're a DIY enthusiast or just need basic transportation on a tight budget, this could be your opportunity. Sold as-is, priced accordingly. Come take a look! \ud83d\udee0\ufe0f",
