    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is listed honestly in fair condition \u2014 it runs and drives, but buyers should go in with realistic expectations. The exterior shows noticeable wear including visible scratches, scuffs, and some paint fading consistent with a vehicle that has seen regular use without premium upkeep. The interior is functional but worn, with some staining on the upholstery and minor trim pieces showing age. Mechanically, the car is operational though it may benefit from some attention \u2014 we recommend a pre-purchase inspection so you know exactly what you're buying. This is a practical, budget-conscious option for a buyer who wants reliable transportation and doesn't mind putting a little work in.",
